<lb ed="X" n="0433a03"/><list><item id="itemX57p0433a0301">止觀搜要記十卷</item><item id="itemX57p0433a0308">涅槃後分疏一卷<note place="inline">下同</note></item>
<lb ed="X" n="0433a04"/><item id="itemX57p0433a0401">授菩薩戒文</item><item id="itemX57p0433a0406">止觀文句</item>
<lb ed="X" n="0433a05"/><item id="itemX57p0433a0501">方等補闕儀</item></list></item></list>
<lb ed="X" n="0433a06"/><p id="pX57p0433a0601">右具在前。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0433a07"/><p id="pX57p0433a0701" rend="margin-left:1em">洪武五年九月　日　　瓦官　克勤　具</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0433a08"/><list><item id="itemX57p0433a0801">天台傳列祖
<lb ed="X" n="0433a09"/><list><item id="itemX57p0433a0901">高祖龍樹尊者</item><item id="itemX57p0433a0907">二祖北齊尊者</item>
<lb ed="X" n="0433a10"/><item id="itemX57p0433a1001">三祖南嶽尊者</item><item id="itemX57p0433a1007">四祖天台智者大師</item>
